Name: S.E.C.U.
About the game: S.E.C.U. is an arcade zombie first person shooter. Features (As of version 0.1.0) : - 4 Horde Mode Maps - 3 Bosses - 12 Weapons - Over 20 Weapon Starter Cards To Unlock - Firing Range Fight your way through 20 waves of zombies and fight a boss at the end, Unlock and choose your loadout! Buy better weapons from walls! Upgrade yourself with perks! Buy better decked out weapons in mystery crate!
